 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"http://www.socialtwist.com\" title=\"SocialTwist\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ESocialTwist\u003C/a\u003E is a customer acquisition platform that creates social referrals for leading brands, retailers, publishers.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EMore than 40 leading brands use the SocialTwist platform to drive social referrals and generate new business.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EThe platform builds and integrates social referral processes and technology into marketing programs. The platform has been tried and tested across hundreds of dissimilar campaigns involving acquisition, rewards, loyalty and various other program objectives. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EThe platform resolves complex issues around privacy, compliance, security, scalability, and fraud management - show-stopper issues for leading brands and merchants. The system is designed to handle the massive transaction volumes generated by viral social campaigns for very large customers.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003Evia: \u003Ca href=\"http://www.socialtwist.com\" title=\"SocialTwist\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ESocialTwist\u003C/a\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
